title: Pilot
description: Dan Rowan and Dick Martin host a Laugh-In. Along with Barbara Feldon, Pamela Austin, Judy Carne, Ken Berry, Herny Gibson, Larry Hovis and others. With segments likle "Cocktail Party", "New Talent Department, "Mod Mod Mod Mod World", "The News From 1987" and a little history. With the success of the special, it made a hit show in 1968.

title: Episode #2.19
description: This Valentine's Day theme show features teen heartthrob Davy Jones of The Monkees.

title: Episode #3.4
description: This week's show features the final television appearance of The Monkees, by this time reduced to a trio.
